title: Air Jordan 1 '85 Neutral Grey
desc: With so many outstanding releases already in the books, the Air Jordan 1 – in its various forms, will once again be a top prize of the year. Undoubtedly high on the list of must-haves is the Air Jordan 1 Hi ’85 “Neutral Grey”, Jordan Brand’s true-to-the-original remake of the white/grey pairing that first landed in stores back in 1985. The Hi ’85 trim was first introduced in February of 2020 as part of the New Beginnings Pack as Jordan Brand unleashed its most accurate rendition of the globally popular sneaker, but the Neutral Grey marks the first such release of an original colorway.
